race.comment: NOLA KEEPING (5) is coming off a 3 length fourth but in a fast 29.74 at Dubbo over 516m. Expected to go close if runs up to latest time. DAKOTA RYLEN (3) rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (30.80) at this track over 530m. Hard to beat again. NATIONAL GRID (1) is better than last start when sixth (23.03) from Box 4 at Murray Bridge over 395m. Boasts a strong record from this draw with four wins and three minor placings from eight starts. Cannot be taken lightly. FERRERO GIRL (2) is likely to have admirers.
